    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and made sure it stayed totally spotless. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
