    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 era. It features a pristine mechanical profile, including proactive rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators to ensure long-term reliability. The 8,400 RPM redline is accessible through a crisp, short-throw six-speed manual gearbox delivering power to the rear wheels via a perfectly calibrated M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, with no signs of subframe stress, and the suspension geometry remains within factory specifications. Finished in a deep gloss with zero paint correction required, the interior is equally impressive, featuring unworn Novillo leather and a dash free of UV degradation. This is a turnkey, investment-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who values linear power delivery and mechanical transparency.",
